summary: Respawn Reveals Its Star Wars Game, Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order
title: Respawn Reveals Its Star Wars Game, Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order
excerpt: During the EA Play presentation, Respawn’s CEO, Vice Zampella, formally announced the studio’s forthcoming Star Wars game. Thus far, the new game from the Titanfall developer has a titl…
description: Zampella says the title is set in the period between Revenge of the Sith and A New Hope, which is an era termed the “Dark Times.” The unnamed protagonist will allow players to control a lightsaber-wielding Padawan who survived Order 66–the event that begat the destruction of the Jedi Order.
